Task
Have I lost my way?
The city can be reached by one of two roads: road number 1 or road number 95. 
You are driving along the road number roadNumber. Can you take this road to the city?
change the variable named roadNumber and assign it the value of the approaching number (road numbers). 
change the isRightRoad variable and set it to a boolean expression that will be true if the number of roads is 1 or 95 , and false if the case exists.

Solution
const roadNumber = 5;
const isRightRoad = roadNumber === 1 || road_number === 95;
